### 5. Dependency Vulnerabilities

- [ ] No known critical CVEs in direct dependencies
- [ ] Dependency lock files are committed and up to date
- [ ] Automated vulnerability scanning is configured in CI
- [ ] Any CVE exceptions are documented with rationale

