## How to Customize This Checklist

1. **Replace the `<!-- PROJECT-SPECIFIC EXAMPLE -->` blocks** with your actual project requirements
2. **Remove irrelevant sections** (e.g., remove SPARQL if you don't use it)
3. **Add domain-specific items** relevant to your industry (healthcare, finance, etc.)
4. **Rename this file** from `security-checklist.md.template` to `security-checklist.md` after customization

